data.title: DejaVu Fonts
data.text:
Bugs and requests

Bugs and requests can be filed in our issue tracker on GitHub.

When requesting new characters please look them up on Unicode Charts and refer to their codes.

Contact us

Send your questions to the dejavu-fonts mailing list. This list is also used for discussions and announcements.

We have our own IRC channel on irc.freenode.org where you can ask all your questions to the developers: #dejavu.

Join us

Join our team! We are always looking for more developers.

The Developerâ€™s Corner has more information for contributors.
